{"fixed_xml":"<ITEM>2. Bey Herrn Euler dem Buchbinder am Rheinsprung ist zu erfragen, wo folgende Bücher iraisonablem Preis zu haben seyen :
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Janii & Tremellii Biblia cum Annotationibus</TITLE>
  </BIBL>;
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Acta Eruditorum Lipsiensia</TITLE> de An. <YEAR>1738</YEAR>. & <YEAR>1739</YEAR>.
  </BIBL>
  <BIBL>
    <AUTHOR>Mohemii</AUTHOR>
    <TITLE>Institutiones histor. Christ.</TITLE> maiores <VOLUME>1. Seculi</VOLUME>, samtl. in <FORMAT>4to</FORMAT>.
  </BIBL>
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Titus Livius</TITLE> ex Editione <AUTHOR>Joannis Clerici</AUTHOR>
  </BIBL>;
  <BIBL>
    <AUTHOR>Ovidii</AUTHOR>
    <TITLE>Tristiam & Epistolae ex Ponto</TITLE> mit <AUTHOR>Sinceri</AUTHOR> Anmerckungen
  </BIBL>;
  <BIBL>
    <AUTHOR>Herodianus</AUTHOR> Graece & Latine cum notis <AUTHOR>Bocceri</AUTHOR>
  </BIBL>;
  <BIBL>
    <AUTHOR>Elianus</AUTHOR> Graece & Latine cum notis <AUTHOR>Schefferi</AUTHOR>
  </BIBL>;
  <BIBL>
    <AUTHOR>Schrevelii</AUTHOR>
    <TITLE>Lexicon Graeco Latinum & Lat. Graec.</TITLE>
  </BIBL>;
  <BIBL>
    <AUTHOR>Nisselii</AUTHOR>
    <TITLE>Biblia Hebraea</TITLE>
  </BIBL>;
  und
  <BIBL>
    <AUTHOR>Buxtorfii</AUTHOR>
    <TITLE>Lexicon</TITLE>, samtl. in <FORMAT>8vo</FORMAT>.
  </BIBL>
</ITEM>","number_of_corrections":9,"explanation":"1) Added missing </BIBL> end-tag for the Mohemii entry so that all BIBL elements are properly nested.
2) Escaped six literal ampersands to & to comply with XML syntax.
3) Replaced the garbled character sequences “4t√≤” and “8v√≤” with “4to” and “8vo” inside the FORMAT elements.
These changes make the fragment well-formed UTF-8 XML."}
